flowchart TD
    Start([Customer buka /cek-status])

    Start --> Source{Dari mana?}

    Source -->|WhatsApp link| SignedURL["GET /cek-status/cari?<br>order_number=...&phone=...<br>&signature=..."]

    SignedURL --> VerifySign{Verifikasi signed URL?}
    VerifySign -->|Invalid / Expired| RejectSign([Tampilkan error:<br>Link tidak valid/kadaluwarsa])
    VerifySign -->|Valid| AutoLookup[Auto-lookup:<br>order_number + phone]

    Source -->|Manual| ShowForm[Tampilkan form:<br>Order Number + Telepon]
    ShowForm --> SubmitForm[POST /cek-status]
    SubmitForm --> RateLimit{Rate limit?<br>5 hit/menit/IP}
    RateLimit -->|Terlampaui| RateError([HTTP 429 Too Many Requests])
    RateLimit -->|OK| ManualLookup[Lookup:<br>order_number + phone]

    AutoLookup --> FindOrder{Cari order}
    ManualLookup --> FindOrder

    FindOrder --> Found{Order ditemukan?}
    Found -->|Tidak| NotFound([Tampilkan:<br>Pesanan tidak ditemukan])
    Found -->|Ya| ShowStatus[Tampilkan detail pesanan:<br>status, items, tracking,<br>timeline status log]

    ShowStatus --> ShowActions{Status = Pending?}

    ShowActions -->|Ya| BatalBtn[Tampilkan tombol Batalkan]
    BatalBtn --> CancelClick[Customer klik Batalkan]
    CancelClick --> ConfirmBatal[Konfirmasi modal]
    ConfirmBatal -->|Batal| ShowStatus
    ConfirmBatal -->|Ya| DoCancel[POST /orders/order/cancel]
    DoCancel --> CancelTransition[TransitionOrderStatus → Cancel]
    CancelTransition --> ReleaseStock[release_reserved]
    ReleaseStock --> RefreshStatus[Refresh halaman]

    ShowActions -->|Bukan Pending| InfoOnly[Tampilkan info:<br>hubungi WA admin untuk perubahan]


